# Agent runtime config. NO inline comments after values (the loader keeps everything after '=').
# Orchestrator: a manager agent that runs its own mission AND graduates sub-agents by writing specs to
# its /graduation queue (a host watcher builds + starts them; the manager never touches docker). Mount
# the graduation queue rw ONLY into this deployment — that mount topology is what makes it the sole
# spawner. RUNTIME_MODE=daemon + a long heartbeat keep it event-driven; it mainly wakes on operator/chat
# messages and sub-agent escalations (avoid a hot recurring loop on an expensive model).
AGENT_ID=orchestrator
BRAIN=claude
MODEL=claude-opus-4-8
RUNTIME_MODE=daemon
INTERVAL_SECONDS=86400
PERMISSION=dangerous
TOOLS_ROOT=/workspace
